{"title":"天山下的新城——素描三幅","authors":["顾工"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":4,"day":25}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"天山下的新城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——素描三幅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顾工"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"行人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她那绣金的小帽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斜插着斑烂的羽毛；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她把彩色的纽扣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缀满自己的胸腰。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哈族有哈族的装束，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"维族有维族的爱好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但是她们肩并肩地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿过那林荫大道……。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"居民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长江南岸的女工，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"结识了新疆的牧童；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们以音韵不同的言语，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汇合成同一节拍的笑声。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晨光叩开了家家门户，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜色关不住透亮的窗台。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们一起到工地上去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们一起从俱乐部归来……。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"医疗站"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有多少朵白色的花啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但那一朵能比她们更美？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"护士的双手像是花瓣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"医生的目光像是花蕊。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有飘忽的芬芳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有甜蜜的汁液；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她们给农民第二次生命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她们给牧人新鲜的热血。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}